">您理解并同意，我们将使用您的订单信息来进行您的身份核验、确定交易、支付结算，为您查询订单，提供客服咨询与售后服务等；我们可能还会使用您的订单信息来判断您的交易是否存在异常以保护您的交易安全。</span></span></span></strong>\n        &nbsp; &nbsp;\n    </p>\n    <p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:56px;line-height:24px\">\n        <strong><span\n                style=\";font-family:楷体;color:#000000;letter-spacing:0;font-weight:bold;font-style:normal;font-size:14px\">2)</span></strong><span\n            style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;color:#000000;letter-spacing:0;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-size:9px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><strong><span\n                style=\";font-family:楷体;color:#000000;letter-spacing:0;font-weight:bold;font-style:normal;font-size:14px\"><span\n                    style=\"font-family:楷体\">支付信息</span></span></strong>\n        &nbsp; &nbsp;\n    </p>\n    <p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:33px;text-indent:0;line-height:24px\">\n        <span\n            style=\";font-family:楷体;color:#000000;letter-spacing:0;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-size:14px\"><span\n                style=\"font-family:楷体\">在您下单后，您可通过</span></span><span\n            style=\";font-family:楷体;color:#000000;letter-spacing:0;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-size:14px\"><span\n                style=\"font-family:楷体\">紫色名片</span></span><span\n            style=\";font-family:楷体;color:#000000;letter-spacing:0;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-size:14px\"><span\n                style=\"font-family:楷体\">系统支持的第三方支付机构完成支付，支付功能本身并不收集您的个人信息，</span></span><strong><span\n                style=\"text-decoration:underline;\"><span\n                    style=\";font-family:楷体;color:#000000;letter-spacing:0;font-weight:bold;text-underline:single;font-style:normal;font-size:14px\"><span\n                        style=\"font-family:楷体\">但我们需将您的订单号、交易金额等与您选择的支付机构共享以实现其确认您的支付指令并完成支付。</span></span></span></strong>\n        &nbsp; &nbsp;\n    </p>\n    <p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:56px;line-height:24px\">\n        <strong><span\n                style=\";font-family:楷体;color:#000000;letter-spacing:0;font-weight:bold;font-style:normal;font-size:14px\">3)</span></strong><span\n            style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;color:#000000;letter-spacing:0;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-size:9px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><strong><span\n                style=\";font-family:楷体;color:#000000;letter-spacing:0;font-weight:bold;font-style:normal;font-size:14px\"><span\n                    style=\"font-family:楷体\">客服与</span>/售后服务所需信息</span></strong>\n        &nbsp; &nbsp;\n    </p>\n    <p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:38px;text-indent:0;line-height:24px\">\n        <strong><span style=\"text-decoration:underline;\"><span\n                    style=\";font-family:楷体;color:#000000;letter-spacing:0;font-weight:bold;text-underline:single;font-style:normal;font-size:14px\"><span\n                        style=\"font-family:楷体\">我们的客服和售后功能会使用您的账户信息和订单信息</span></span></span></strong><span\n            style=\";font-family:楷体;color:#000000;letter-spacing:0;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-size:14px\"><span\n                style=\"font-family:楷体\">。为保证您的账户安全，我们的客服会使用您的账户信息核验您的身份。当您需要使用客服或售后功能时，我们会查询您的订单信息。</span></span><strong><span\n                style=\"text-decoration:underline;\"><span\n                    style=\";font-family:楷体;color:#000000;letter-spacing:0;font-weight:bold;text-underline:single;font-style:normal;font-size:14px\"><span\n                        style=\"font-family:楷体\">在与我们的客服人员沟通时，您可能还需要提供上述信息之外的其他信息，如当您要求变更配送地址、联系人或联系电话等。</span></span></span></strong>\n        &nbsp; &nbsp;\n    </p>\n    <p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:56px;line-height:24px\">\n        <strong><span\n                style=\";font-family:楷体;color:#000000;letter-spacing:0;font-weight:bold;font-style:normal;font-size:14px\">4)</span></strong><span\n            style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;color:#000000;letter-spacing:0;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-size:9px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><strong><span\n                style=\";font-family:楷体;color:#000000;letter-spacing:0;font-weight:bold;font-style:normal;font-size:14px\"><span\n                    style=\"font-family:楷体\">保障交易安全所需信息</span></span></strong>\n        &nbsp; &nbsp;\n    </p>\n    <p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:38px;text-indent:0;line-height:24px\">\n        <strong><span style=\"text-decoration:underline;\"><span\n                    style=\";font-family:楷体;color:#000000;letter-spacing:0;font-weight:bold;text-underline:single;font-style:normal;font-size:14px\"><span\n                        style=\"font-family:楷体\">为确认交易状态及为您提供售后与争议解决服务，我们须通过您基于交易所确定的交易对象、第三方支付机构、物流公司等收集与交易进度相关的您的交易、支付、物流信息，或将您的交易信息共享给上述服务提供者。</span></span></span></strong>\n        &nbsp; &nbsp;\n    </p>\n    <p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:47px;line-height:24px\">\n        <strong><span\n                style=\";font-family:楷体;color:#000000;letter-spacing:0;font-weight:bold;font-style:normal;font-size:14px\">2.2.4.</span></strong><span\n            style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;color:#000000;letter-spacing:0;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-size:9px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><strong><span\n                style=\";font-family:楷体;color:#000000;letter-spacing:0;font-weight:bold;font-style:normal;font-size:14px\"><span\n                    style=\"font-family:楷体\">优化产品与</span>/服务所需信息</span></strong>\n        &nbsp; &nbsp;\n    </p>\n    <p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:47px;text-indent:0;line-height:24px\">\n        <strong><span style=\"text-decoration:underline;\"><span\n                    style=\";font-family:楷体;color:#000000;letter-spacing:0;font-weight:bold;text-underline:single;font-style:normal;font-size:14px\"><span\n                        style=\"font-family:楷体\">我们可能会收集您的订单信息、浏览记录、浏览习惯等进行数据分析以描述用户特征，用来为您展示或推荐您感兴趣的商品或服务信息。</span></span></span></strong><span\n            style=\";font-family:楷体;color:#000000;letter-spacing:0;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-size:14px\"><span\n                style=\"font-family:楷体\">除上述信息外，</span></span><strong><span style=\"text-decoration:underline;\"><span\n                    style=\";font-family:楷体;color:#000000;letter-spacing:0;font-weight:bold;text-underline:single;font-style:normal;font-size:14px\"><span\n                        style=\"font-family:楷体\">我们还可能为提供服务或改进服务质量的合理需要而收集您的其他信息，包括您与我们的客服联系时提供的信息，您参与问卷调查时向我们发送的信息等。我们可能会将来自某项服务的信息与来自其他服务的信息结合起来，以便为您提供服务、个性化内容和建议。对于从您的各种设备上收集到的信息，我们可能会将它们进行关联，以便我们能在这些设备上为您提供一致的服务。</span></span></span></strong>\n        &nbsp; &nbsp;\n    </p>\n    <p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:47px;line-height:24px\">\n        <strong><span\n                style=\";font-family:楷体;color:#000000;letter-spacing:0;font-weight:bold;font-style:normal;font-size:14px\">2.2.5.</span></strong><span\n            style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;color:#000000;letter-spacing:0;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-size:9px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><strong><span\n                style=\";font-family:楷体;color:#000000;letter-spacing:0;font-weight:bold;font-style:normal;font-size:14px\"><span\n                    style=\"font-family:楷体\">保障账户安全所需信息</span></span></strong>\n        &nbsp; &nbsp;\n    </p>\n    <p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:47px;text-indent:0;line-height:24px\">\n        <span\n            style=\";font-family:楷体;color:#000000;letter-spacing:0;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-size:14px\"><span\n                style=\"font-family:楷体\">为提高您使用</span></span><span\n            style=\";font-family:楷体;color:#000000;letter-spacing:0;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-size:14px\"><span\n                style=\"font-family:楷体\">紫色名片</span></span><span\n            style=\";font-family:楷体;color:#000000;letter-spacing:0;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-size:14px\"><span\n                style=\"font-family:楷体\">服务的安全性，更准确地预防钓鱼网站欺诈和保护账户安全，</span></span><strong><span\n                style=\"text-decoration:underline;\"><span\n                    style=\";font-family:楷体;color:#000000;letter-spacing:0;font-weight:bold;text-underline:single;font-style:normal;font-size:14px\"><span\n                        style=\"font-family:楷体\">我们可能会通过了解您的订单信息、浏览记录、浏览习惯、常用软件信息、设备信息等来判断您账户的风险，并可能会记录一些我们认为有风险的链接（</span>“URL”）。</span></span></strong>\n        &nbsp; &nbsp;\n    </p>\n    <p style=\"text-align:justify;margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:38px;text-justify:inter-ideograph\"\n        align=\"justify\">\n        <strong><span\n                style=\";font-family:楷体;color:#000000;letter-spacing:0;font-weight:bold;font-style:normal;font-size:14px\">2.3.</span></strong><span\n            style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;color:#000000;letter-spacing:0;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-size:9px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><strong><span\n                style=\";font-family:楷体;color:#000000;letter-spacing:0;font-weight:bold;font-style:normal;font-size:14px\"><span\n                    style=\"font-family:楷体\">用户可选择是否授权收集、使用的信息</span></span></strong>\n        &nbsp; &nbsp;\n    </p>\n    <p style=\"text-align:justify;margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:38px;text-indent:0;text-justify:inter-ideograph\"\n        align=\"justify\">\n        <span style=\";font-family:楷体;color:#000000;letter-spacing:0;font-style:normal;font-size:14px\"><span\n                style=\"font-family:楷体\">为向您提供更加优质、满意、个性化的服务，努力提升您的用户体验，我们可能会附加收集和使用您的信息。若您不提供这些信息，您依然可以获得</span></span><span\n            style=\";font-family:楷体;color:#000