e:single;font-style:normal;font-size:14px\"><span\n                        style=\"font-family:楷体\">如上述，</span></span></span></strong><strong><span\n                style=\"text-decoration:underline;\"><span\n                    style=\";font-family:楷体;color:#000000;letter-spacing:0;font-weight:bold;text-underline:single;font-style:normal;font-size:14px\"><span\n                        style=\"font-family:楷体\">紫色名片</span></span></span></strong><strong><span\n                style=\"text-decoration:underline;\"><span\n                    style=\";font-family:楷体;color:#000000;letter-spacing:0;font-weight:bold;text-underline:single;font-style:normal;font-size:14px\"><span\n                        style=\"font-family:楷体\">将使用各种安全技术、程序和制度防止用户个人信息的丢失、不当使用、未经授权的阅览或披露。但您充分理解并同意：由于技术的限制以及可能存在的各种恶意手段，在互联网行业，即便竭尽所能加强安全措施，也不可能始终保证信息百分之百的安全。</span></span></span></strong>\n        &nbsp; &nbsp;\n    </p>\n    <p style=\"text-align:justify;margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:9px;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:24px\"\n        align=\"justify\">\n        <span\n            style=\"font-family:楷体;color:#000000;letter-spacing:0;font-weight:bold;font-style:normal;font-size:16px\">&nbsp;</span><strong><span\n                style=\";font-family:楷体;color:#000000;letter-spacing:0;font-weight:bold;font-style:normal;font-size:14px\">&nbsp;</span></strong><span\n            style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;color:#000000;letter-spacing:0;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-size:9px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span\n            style=\";font-family:楷体;color:#000000;letter-spacing:0;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-size:14px\"><span\n                style=\"font-family:楷体\">在不幸发生个人信息安全事件后，我们将按照法律法规的要求向您告知：安全事件的基本情况和可能的影响、我们已采取或将要采取的处置措施、您可自主防范和降低风险的建议、对您的补救措施等。事件相关情况我们将以信函、电话、推送通知等方式告知您，难以逐一告知个人信息主体时，我们会采取合理、有效的方式发布公告。同时，我们还将按照监管部门要求，上报个人信息安全事件的处置情况。</span></span>\n        &nbsp; &nbsp;\n    </p>\n    <p style=\"text-align:justify;margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:38px;text-indent:0;text-justify:inter-ideograph\"\n        align=\"justify\">\n        <span style=\";font-family:楷体;color:#000000;letter-spacing:0;font-style:normal;font-size:14px\">&nbsp;</span>\n        &nbsp; &nbsp;\n    </p>\n    <p style=\"text-align:justify;margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:21px;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:24px\"\n        align=\"justify\">\n        <span\n            style=\"font-family:楷体;color:#000000;letter-spacing:0;font-weight:bold;font-style:normal;font-size:16px\">1.&nbsp;</span><strong><span\n                style=\";font-family:楷体;color:#000000;letter-spacing:0;font-weight:bold;font-style:normal;font-size:14px\"><span\n                    style=\"font-family:楷体\">用户个人信息的保存、访问和管理</span></span></strong>\n        &nbsp; &nbsp;\n    </p>\n    <p style=\"text-align:justify;margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:9px;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:24px\"\n        align=\"justify\">\n        <span\n            style=\"font-family:楷体;color:#000000;letter-spacing:0;font-weight:bold;font-style:normal;font-size:16px\">&nbsp;</span><strong><span\n                style=\";font-family:楷体;color:#000000;letter-spacing:0;font-weight:bold;font-style:normal;font-size:14px\">&nbsp;</span></strong><span\n            style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;color:#000000;letter-spacing:0;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-size:9px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><strong><span\n                style=\";font-family:楷体;color:#000000;letter-spacing:0;font-weight:bold;font-style:normal;font-size:14px\"><span\n                    style=\"font-family:楷体\">用户个人信息的保存</span></span></strong>\n        &nbsp; &nbsp;\n    </p>\n    <p style=\"text-align:justify;margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:38px;text-indent:0;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:24px\"\n        align=\"justify\">\n        <span style=\";font-family:楷体;color:#000000;letter-spacing:0;font-style:normal;font-size:14px\"><span\n                style=\"font-family:楷体\">您的个人信息将全部被存储于中华人民共和国境内，但以下情形除外：</span></span>\n        &nbsp; &nbsp;\n    </p>\n    <p style=\"text-align:justify;margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:47px;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:24px\"\n        align=\"justify\">\n        <strong><span\n                style=\";font-family:楷体;color:#000000;letter-spacing:0;font-weight:bold;font-style:normal;font-size:14px\">6.1.1.</span></strong><span\n            style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;color:#000000;letter-spacing:0;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-size:9px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span\n            style=\";font-family:楷体;color:#000000;letter-spacing:0;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-size:14px\"><span\n                style=\"font-family:楷体\">法律法规另有明确规定；</span></span>\n        &nbsp; &nbsp;\n    </p>\n    <p style=\"text-align:justify;margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:47px;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:24px\"\n        align=\"justify\">\n        <strong><span\n                style=\";font-family:楷体;color:#000000;letter-spacing:0;font-weight:bold;font-style:normal;font-size:14px\">6.1.2.</span></strong><span\n            style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;color:#000000;letter-spacing:0;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-size:9px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span\n            style=\";font-family:楷体;color:#000000;letter-spacing:0;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-size:14px\"><span\n                style=\"font-family:楷体\">获得您的明确授权；</span></span>\n        &nbsp; &nbsp;\n    </p>\n    <p style=\"text-align:justify;margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:47px;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:24px\"\n        align=\"justify\">\n        <strong><span\n                style=\";font-family:楷体;color:#000000;letter-spacing:0;font-weight:bold;font-style:normal;font-size:14px\">6.1.3.</span></strong><span\n            style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;color:#000000;letter-spacing:0;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-size:9px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span\n            style=\";font-family:楷体;color:#000000;letter-spacing:0;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-size:14px\"><span\n                style=\"font-family:楷体\">您通过互联网进行跨境交易等个人主动行为；</span></span>\n        &nbsp; &nbsp;\n    </p>\n    <p style=\"text-align:justify;margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:47px;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:24px\"\n        align=\"justify\">\n        <strong><span\n                style=\";font-family:楷体;color:#000000;letter-spacing:0;font-weight:bold;font-style:normal;font-size:14px\">6.1.4.</span></strong><span\n            style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;color:#000000;letter-spacing:0;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-size:9px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span\n            style=\";font-family:楷体;color:#000000;letter-spacing:0;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-size:14px\"><span\n                style=\"font-family:楷体\">针对以上情形，我们会依据本政策及相关法律法规对您的个人信息提供保护。</span></span>\n        &nbsp; &nbsp;\n    </p>\n    <p style=\"text-align:justify;margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:38px;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:24px\"\n        align=\"justify\">\n        <strong><span\n                style=\";font-family:楷体;color:#000000;letter-spacing:0;font-weight:bold;font-style:normal;font-size:14px\">6.2.</span></strong><span\n            style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;color:#000000;letter-spacing:0;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-size:9px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><strong><span\n                style=\";font-family:楷体;color:#000000;letter-spacing:0;font-weight:bold;font-style:normal;font-size:14px\"><span\n                    style=\"font-family:楷体\">用户个人信息的访问</span></span></strong>\n      