ong><span\n                style=\";font-family:楷体;color:#000000;letter-spacing:0;font-weight:bold;font-style:normal;font-size:14px\">6.2.2.</span></strong><span\n            style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;color:#000000;letter-spacing:0;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-size:9px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><strong><span\n                style=\";font-family:楷体;color:#000000;letter-spacing:0;font-weight:bold;font-style:normal;font-size:14px\"><span\n                    style=\"font-family:楷体\">搜索信息</span>—</span></strong><span\n            style=\";font-family:楷体;color:#000000;letter-spacing:0;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-size:14px\">—您可登录账号通过“搜索”访问或清除您的搜索记录。</span>\n        &nbsp; &nbsp;\n    </p>\n    <p style=\"text-align:justify;margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:47px;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:24px\"\n        align=\"justify\">\n        <strong><span\n                style=\";font-family:楷体;color:#000000;letter-spacing:0;font-weight:bold;font-style:normal;font-size:14px\">6.2.3.</span></strong><span\n            style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;color:#000000;letter-spacing:0;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-size:9px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><strong><span\n                style=\";font-family:楷体;color:#000000;letter-spacing:0;font-weight:bold;font-style:normal;font-size:14px\"><span\n                    style=\"font-family:楷体\">浏览信息</span></span></strong><span\n            style=\";font-family:楷体;color:#000000;letter-spacing:0;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-size:14px\">——您可登陆账号通过“个人中心-我的足迹”访问或清除您的浏览记录。</span>\n        &nbsp; &nbsp;\n    </p>\n    <p style=\"text-align:justify;margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:47px;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:24px\"\n        align=\"justify\">\n        <strong><span\n                style=\";font-family:楷体;color:#000000;letter-spacing:0;font-weight:bold;font-style:normal;font-size:14px\">6.2.4.</span></strong><span\n            style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;color:#000000;letter-spacing:0;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-size:9px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><strong><span\n                style=\";font-family:楷体;color:#000000;letter-spacing:0;font-weight:bold;font-style:normal;font-size:14px\"><span\n                    style=\"font-family:楷体\">订单信息：</span></span></strong><span\n            style=\";font-family:楷体;color:#000000;letter-spacing:0;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-size:14px\"><span\n                style=\"font-family:楷体\">您可登录账号通过</span>“个人中心-我的订单”访问或清除您的订单记录、拼单记录、交易记录等。</span>\n        &nbsp; &nbsp;\n    </p>\n    <p style=\"text-align:justify;margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:47px;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:24px\"\n        align=\"justify\">\n        <strong><span\n                style=\";font-family:楷体;color:#000000;letter-spacing:0;font-weight:bold;font-style:normal;font-size:14px\">6.2.5.</span></strong><span\n            style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;color:#000000;letter-spacing:0;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-size:9px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><strong><span\n                style=\"text-decoration:underline;\"><span\n                    style=\";font-family:楷体;color:#000000;letter-spacing:0;font-weight:bold;text-underline:single;font-style:normal;font-size:14px\"><span\n                        style=\"font-family:楷体\">若您无法通过上述路径访问该等信息，您可通过</span></span></span></strong><strong><span\n                style=\"text-decoration:underline;\"><span\n                    style=\";font-family:楷体;color:#000000;letter-spacing:0;font-weight:bold;text-underline:single;font-style:normal;font-size:14px\"><span\n                        style=\"font-family:楷体\">紫色名片</span></span></span></strong><strong><span\n                style=\"text-decoration:underline;\"><span\n                    style=\";font-family:楷体;color:#000000;letter-spacing:0;font-weight:bold;text-underline:single;font-style:normal;font-size:14px\"><span\n                        style=\"font-family:楷体\">客服与我们联系。对于您在使用我们的产品或服务过程中产生的其他个人信息，我们将根据第</span>6.5条“响应您的上述请求”中的相关安排向您提供。</span></span></strong>\n        &nbsp; &nbsp;\n    </p>\n    <p style=\"text-align:justify;margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:38px;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:24px\"\n        align=\"justify\">\n        <strong><span\n                style=\";font-family:楷体;color:#000000;letter-spacing:0;font-weight:bold;font-style:normal;font-size:14px\">6.3.</span></strong><span\n            style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;color:#000000;letter-spacing:0;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-size:9px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><strong><span\n                style=\";font-family:楷体;color:#000000;letter-spacing:0;font-weight:bold;font-style:normal;font-size:14px\"><span\n                    style=\"font-family:楷体\">用户个人信息的更正、补充</span></span></strong>\n        &nbsp; &nbsp;\n    </p>\n    <p style=\"text-align:justify;margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:38px;text-indent:0;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:24px\"\n        align=\"justify\">\n        <span style=\";font-family:楷体;color:#000000;letter-spacing:0;font-style:normal;font-size:14px\"><span\n                style=\"font-family:楷体\">当您发现您的个人信息有误或需要补充时，您可通过</span>“6.2用户个人信息的访问”中列明的方式提出更正或补充申请。</span>\n        &nbsp; &nbsp;\n    </p>\n    <p style=\"text-align:justify;margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:38px;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:24px\"\n        align=\"justify\">\n        <strong><span\n                style=\";font-family:楷体;color:#000000;letter-spacing:0;font-weight:bold;font-style:normal;font-size:14px\">6.4.</span></strong><span\n            style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;color:#000000;letter-spacing:0;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-size:9px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><strong><span\n                style=\";font-family:楷体;color:#000000;letter-spacing:0;font-weight:bold;font-style:normal;font-size:14px\"><span\n                    style=\"font-family:楷体\">用户个人信息的删除</span></span></strong>\n        &nbsp; &nbsp;\n    </p>\n    <p style=\"text-align:justify;margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:28px;text-indent:0;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:24px\"\n        align=\"justify\">\n        <span style=\";font-family:楷体;color:#000000;letter-spacing:0;font-style:normal;font-size:14px\"><span\n                style=\"font-family:楷体\">您可通过</span>“6.2用户个人信息的访问”中列明的方式删除您的部分个人信息。</span>\n        &nbsp; &nbsp;\n    </p>\n    <p style=\"text-align:justify;margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:28px;text-indent:0;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:24px\"\n        align=\"justify\">\n        <span style=\";font-family:楷体;color:#000000;letter-spacing:0;font-style:normal;font-size:14px\"><span\n                style=\"font-family:楷体\">在以下情形中，您可向我们提出删除个人信息的请求：</span></span>\n        &nbsp; &nbsp;\n    </p>\n    <p style=\"text-align:justify;margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:28px;text-indent:0;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:24px\"\n        align=\"justify\">\n        <span\n            style=\";font-family:楷体;color:#000000;letter-spacing:0;font-style:normal;font-size:14px\">1）我们处理个人信息的行为违反法律法规；</span>\n        &nbsp; &nbsp;\n    </p>\n    <p style=\"text-align:justify;margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:28px;text-indent:0;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:24px\"\n        align=\"justify\">\n        <span\n            style=\";font-family:楷体;color:#000000;letter-spacing:0;font-style:normal;font-size:14px\">2）我们收集、使用您的个人信息，却未征得您的明确同意；</span>\n        &nbsp; &nbsp;\n    </p>\n    <p style=\"text-align:justify;margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:28px;text-indent:0;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:24px\"\n        align=\"justify\">\n        <span\n            style=\";font-family:楷体;color:#000000;letter-spacing:0;font-style:normal;font-size:14px\">3）我们处理个人信息的行为严重违反了与您的约定；</span>\n        &nbsp; &nbsp;\n    </p>\n    <p style=\"text-align:justify;margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:28px;text-indent:0;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:24px\"\n        align=\"justify\">\n        <span\n            style=\";font-family:楷体;color:#000000;letter-spacing:0;font-style:normal;font-size:14px\">4）您不再使用我们的产品或服务；</span>\n        &nbsp; &nbsp;\n    </p>\n    <p style=\"text-align:justify;margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:28px;text-indent:0;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:24px\"\n        align=\"justify\">\n        <span\n            style=\";font-family:楷体;color:#000000;letter-spacing:0;font-style:normal;font-size:14px\">5）我们永久不再为您提供产品或服务。</span>\n        &nbsp; &nbsp;\n    </p>\n    <p style=\"text-align:justify;margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:38px;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:24px\"\n        align=\"justify\">\n        <strong><span\n                style=\";font-family:楷体;color:#000000;letter-spacing:0;font-weight:bold;font-style:normal;font-size:14px\">6.5.</span></strong><span\n            style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;color:#000000;letter-spacing:0;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-size:9px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><strong><span\n                style=\";font-family:楷体;color:#000000;letter-spacing:0;font-weight:bold;font-style:normal;font-size:14px\"><span\n                    style=\"font-family:楷体\">响应您的上述请求</span></span></strong>\n        &nbsp; &nbsp;\n    </p>\n    <p style=\"text-align:justify;margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:28px;text-indent:0;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:24px\"\n        align=\"justify\">\n        <span style=\";font-family:楷体;color:#000000;letter-spacing:0;font-style:normal;font-size:14px\"><span\n                style=\"font-family:楷体\">为保障安全，您可能需要提供书面请求，或以其他方式证明您的身份。我们可能会先要求您验证自己的身份，然后再处理您的请求。对于您合理的请求，我们原则上不收取费用，但对多次重复、超出合理限度的请求，我们将视情况收取一定成本费用。对于那些无端重复、需要过多技术手段（例如，需要开发新系统或从根本上改变现行惯例）、给他人合法权益带来风险或者非常不切实际的请求，我们可能会予以拒绝。</span></span>\n        &nbsp; &nbsp;\n    </p>\n    <p style=\"text-align:justify;margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:38px;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:24px\"\n        align=\"justify\">\n        <strong><span\n                style=\";font-family:楷体;color:#000000;letter-spacing:0;font-weight:bold;font-style:normal;font-size:14px\">6.6.</span></strong><span\n            style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;color:#000000;letter-spacing:0;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-size:9px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><strong><span\n                style=\";font-family:楷体;color:#000000;letter-spacing:0;font-weight:bold;font-style:normal;font-size:14px\"><span\n                    style=\"font-family:楷体\">您理解并同意，在以下情形中，按照法律法规的要求，我们将无法响应您的请求：</span></span></strong>\n        &nbsp; &nbsp;\n    </p>\n    <p style=\"text-align:justify;margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:47px;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:24px\"\n        align=\"justify\">\n        <strong><span\n                style=\";font-family:楷体;color:#000000;letter-spacing:0;font-weight:bold;font-style:normal;font-size:14px\">6.6.1.</span></strong><span\n            style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;color:#000000;letter-spacing:0;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-size:9px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span\n            style=\";font-family:楷体;color:#000000;letter-spacing:0;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-size:14px\"><span\n                style=\"font-family:楷体\">与国家安全、国防安全有关的；</span></span>\n        &nbsp; &nbsp;\n    </p>\n    <p style=\"text-align:justify;margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:47px;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:24px\"\n        align=\"justify\">\n        <strong><span\n                style=\";font-family:楷体;color:#000000;letter-spacing:0;font-weight:bold;font-style:normal;font-size:14px\">6.6.2.</span></strong><span\n            style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;color:#000000;letter-spacing:0;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-size:9px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span\n            style=\";font-family:楷体;color:#000000;letter-spacing:0;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-size:14px\"><span\n                style=\"font-family:楷体\">与公共安全、公共卫生、重大公共利益有关的；</span></span>\n        &nbsp; &nbsp;\n    </p>\n    <p style=\"text-align:justify;margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:47px;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:24px\"\n        align=\"justify\">\n        <strong><span\n                style=\";font-family:楷体;color:#000000;letter-spacing:0;font-weight:bold;font-style:normal;font-size:14px\">6.6.3.</span></strong><span\n            style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;color:#000000;letter-spacing:0;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-size:9px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span\n            style=\";font-family:楷体;color:#000000;letter-spacing:0;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-size:14px\"><span\n                style=\"font-family:楷体\">与犯罪侦查、起诉、审判和执行判决等有关的；</span></span>\n        &nbsp; &nbsp;\n    </p>\n    <p style=\"text-align:justify;margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:47px;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:24px\"\n        align=\"justify\">\n        <strong><span\n                style=\";font-family:楷体;color:#000000;letter-spacing:0;font-weight:bold;font-style:normal;font-size:14px\">6.6.4.</span></strong><span\n            style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;color:#000000;letter-spacing:0;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-size:9px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span\n            style=\";font-family:楷体;color:#000000;letter-spacing:0;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-size:14px\"><span\n                style=\"font-family:楷体\">有充分证据表明个人信息主体存在主观恶意或滥用权利的；</span></span>\n        &nbsp; &nbsp;\n    </p>\n    <p style=\"text-align:justify;margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:47px;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:24px\"\n        align=\"justify\">\n        <strong><span\n                style=\";font-family:楷体;color:#000000;letter-spacing:0;font-weight:bold;font-style:normal;font-size:14px\">6.6.5.</span></strong><span\n            style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;color:#000000;letter-spacing:0;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-size:9px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span\n            style=\";font-family:楷体;color:#000000;letter-spacing:0;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-size:14px\"><span\n                style=\"font-family:楷体\">响应您的请求将导致您或其他个人、组织的合法权益受到严重损害的；</span></span>\n        &nbsp; &nbsp;\n    </p>\n    <p style=\"text-align:justify;margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:47px;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:24px\"\n        align=\"justify\">\n        <strong><span\n                style=\";font-family:楷体;color:#000000;letter-spacing:0;font-weight:bold;font-style:normal;font-size:14px\">6.6.6.</span></strong><span\n            style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;color:#000000;letter-spacing:0;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-size:9px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span\n            style=\";font-family:楷体;color:#000000;letter-spacing:0;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-size:14px\"><span\n                style=\"font-family:楷体\">涉及商业秘密的。</span></span>\n        &nbsp; &nbsp;\n    </p>\n    <p style=\"text-align:justify;margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:24px\"\n        align=\"justify\">\n        <span style=\";font-family:楷体;color:#000000;letter-spacing:0;font-style:normal;font-size:14px\">&nbsp;</span>\n        &nbsp; &nbsp;\n    </p>\n    <p style=\"text-align:justify;margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:21px;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:24px\"\n        align=\"justify\">\n        <span\n            style=\"font-family:楷体;color:#000000;letter-spacing:0;font-weight:bold;font-style:normal;font-size:16px\">1.&nbsp;</span><strong><span\n                style=\";font-family:楷体;color:#000000;letter-spacing:0;font-weight:bold;font-style:normal;font-size:14px\"><span\n                    style=\"font-family:楷体\">未成年人信息保护</span></span></strong>\n        &nbsp; &nbsp;\n    </p>\n    <p style=\"text-align:justify;margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:28px;text-indent:0;text-justify:inter-ideograph\"\n        align=\"justify\">\n        <span style=\";font-family:楷体;color:#000000;letter-spacing:0;font-style:normal;font-size:14px\"><span\n                style=\"font-family:楷体\">我们非常重视未成年人的个人信息保护，若您为</span>18周岁以下的未成年人，请您及您的监护人仔细阅读本政策，并在征得您的监护人同意的前提下使用我们的服务或向我们提供信息。</span>\n        &nbsp; &nbsp;\n    </p>\n    <p style=\"text-align:justify;margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:24px\"\n        align=\"justify\">\n        <span style=\";font-family:Calibri;color:#000000;letter-spacing:0;font-style:normal;font-size:14px\">&nbsp;</span>\n        &nbsp; &nbsp;\n    </p>\n    <p style=\"text-align:justify;margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:21px;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:24px\"\n        align=\"justify\">\n        <span\n            style=\"font-family:楷体;color:#000000;letter-spacing:0;font-weight:bold;font-style:normal;font-size:16px\">1.&nbsp;</span><strong><span\n                style=\";font-family:楷体;color:#000000;letter-spacing:0;font-weight:bold;font-style:normal;font-size:14px\"><span\n                    style=\"font-family:楷体\">其他</span></span></strong>\n        &nbsp; &nbsp;\n    </p>\n    <p style=\"text-align:justify;margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:9px;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:24px\"\n        align=\"justify\">\n        <span\n            style=\"font-family:楷体;color:#000000;letter-spacing:0;font-weight:bold;font-style:normal;font-size:16px\">&nbsp;</span><strong><span\n                style=\";font-family:楷体;color:#000000;letter-spacing:0;font-weight:bold;font-style:normal;font-size:14px\">&nbsp;</span></strong><span\n            style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;color:#000000;letter-spacing:0;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-size:9px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><strong><span\n                style=\";font-family:楷体;color:#000000;letter-spacing:0;font-weight:bold;font-style:normal;font-size:14px\"><span\n                    style=\"font-family:楷体\">条款的独立性</span></span></strong>\n        &nbsp; &nbsp;\n    </p>\n    <p style=\"text-align:justify;margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:38px;text-indent:0;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:24px\"\n        align=\"justify\">\n        <span style=\";font-family:楷体;color:#000000;letter-spacing:0;font-style:normal;font-size:14px\"><span\n                style=\"font-family:楷体\">如果根据适用的法律认定本政策中的任何条款或者任何条款中的任何部分无效、违法或者不具有可执行性，这种无效、违法或者不具有可执行性不影响本政策中的任何其它条款或者这些条款中的任何其它部分的效力。</span></span>\n        &nbsp; &nbsp;\n    </p>\n    <p style=\"text-align:justify;margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:38px;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:24px\"\n        align=\"justify\">\n        <strong><span\n                style=\";font-family:楷体;color:#000000;letter-spacing:0;font-weight:bold;font-style:normal;font-size:14px\">8.2.</span></strong><span\n            style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;color:#000000;letter-spacing:0;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-size:9px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><strong><span\n                style=\";font-family:楷体;color:#000000;letter-spacing:0;font-weight:bold;font-style:normal;font-size:14px\"><span\n                    style=\"font-family:楷体\">联系我们</span></span></strong>\n        &nbsp; &nbsp;\n    </p>\n    <p style=\"text-align:justify;margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:38px;text-indent:0;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:24px\"\n        align=\"justify\">\n        <span style=\";font-family:楷体;color:#000000;letter-spacing:0;font-style:normal;font-size:14px\"><span\n                style=\"font-family:楷体\">您对本政策或您的个人信息相关事宜有任何问题、意见或建议，请联系</span></span><span\n            style=\";font-family:楷体;color:#000000;letter-spacing:0;font-style:normal;font-size:14px\"><span\n                style=\"font-family:楷体\">紫色名片</span></span><span\n            style=\";font-family:楷体;color:#000000;letter-spacing:0;font-style:normal;font-size:14px\"><span\n                style=\"font-family:楷体\">客服或通过个人中心</span>“设置”中的“意见反馈”联系我们。</span>\n        &nbsp; &nbsp;\n    </p>\n    <p style=\"text-align:justify;margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:38px;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:24px\"\n        align=\"justify\">\n        <strong><span\n                style=\";font-family:楷体;color:#000000;letter-spacing:0;font-weight:bold;font-style:normal;font-size:14px\">8.3.</span></strong><span\n            style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;color:#000000;letter-spacing:0;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-size:9px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><strong><span\n                style=\";font-family:楷体;color:#000000;letter-spacing:0;font-weight:bold;font-style:normal;font-size:14px\"><span\n                    style=\"font-family:楷体\">生效日期</span></span></strong>\n        &nbsp; &nbsp;\n    </p>\n    <p style=\"text-align:justify;margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:28px;text-indent:7px;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:24px\"\n        align=\"justify\">\n        <span style=\";font-family:楷体;color:#000000;letter-spacing:0;font-style:normal;font-size:14px\"><span\n