an>\r\n</p>\r\n<h1 style=\"margin-right:8px;text-align:left;line-height:18px\">\r\n    <strong><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-weight:bold;font-size:14px\">2.</span></strong><strong> </strong><strong><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-weight:bold;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">协议范围及变更</span></span></strong>\r\n</h1>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:8px;margin-left:8px;text-indent:0;text-align:left;line-height:18px\" align=\"left\">\r\n    <span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:14px\">2.1</span> <strong><span style=\"text-decoration:underline;\"><span style=\";font-family:楷体;letter-spacing:-0;font-weight:bold;text-underline:#000000 single;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">协议范围。</span></span></span></strong><strong><span style=\"text-decoration:underline;\"><span style=\";font-family:楷体;letter-spacing:-0;font-weight:bold;text-underline:#000000 single;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">紫色名片</span></span></span></strong><strong><span style=\"text-decoration:underline;\"><span style=\";font-family:楷体;letter-spacing:-0;font-weight:bold;text-underline:#000000 single;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">规则为本协议不可分割的一部分，与协议正文具有同等法律效力。</span></span></span></strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:8px;margin-left:50px;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\" align=\"justify\">\r\n    <span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:14px\">2.2</span><span style=\";font-family:楷体;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:14px\">&nbsp;</span><strong><span style=\"text-decoration:underline;\"><span style=\";font-family:楷体;letter-spacing:-0;font-weight:bold;text-underline:#000000 single;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">协议变更。为给您提供更好的服务，</span></span></span></strong><strong><span style=\"text-decoration:underline;\"><span style=\";font-family:楷体;letter-spacing:-0;font-weight:bold;text-underline:#000000 single;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">紫色名片</span></span></span></strong><strong><spa