ght:18px\" align=\"left\">\r\n    <span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:12px\">5)</span> <span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">使用</span></span><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">紫色名片</span></span><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">平台外挂和</span></span><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:14px\">/</span><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">或利用</span></span><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">紫色名片</span></span><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">平台当中的</span></span><span style=\";font-family:楷体;letter-spacing:-4px;font-size:14px\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:14px\">BUG</span><span style=\";font-family:楷体;letter-spacing:-4px;font-size:14px\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">来获得不正当的利益；</span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:8px;margin-left:84px;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\" align=\"justify\">\r\n    <span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:12px\">6)</span><span style=\";font-family:楷体;letter-spacing:0;font-size:12px\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">利用劫持域名服务器等技术非法侵入、破坏</span></span><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">紫色名片</span></span><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">平台的服务器软件系统，或</span></span><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:14px\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\";font-family:楷体;letter-spacing:-0;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">者修改、增加、删除、窃取、截留、替换</span></span><span style=\";font-family:楷体;letter-spacing:-0;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">紫色名片</span></span><span style=\";font-family:楷体;letter-spacing:-0;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"fo